high_descs: Turn left to exit the room and walk through the passage to get to the bedroom with the white dresser.
Pick up the book from the dresser.
Turn around and walk out of the room and move left to walk to the brown table.
Turn on the table lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the book under the light of the lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight and turn your right to reach the dresser
Pick up the book from the dresser
Turn back, walk straight and turn your left to reach the desk lamp table
Turn on the desk lamp and examine the book
anns.task_desc: Examine the book by the light of a desk lamp

high_descs: Turn to your left, move straight to the end, turn to your right, go straight towards the table
Pick up the book on the table
Turn to you right, move ahead, again turn to your right, walk straight to the end, turn to your left, and turn to turn right towards the table
Turn on the small lamp on the table
anns.task_desc: Examine the book by the small lamp on the table

high_descs: Enter into the left side room then walk straight and turn towards the left side room which is in the corner, walk straight to enter into the bedroom and reach the dresser.
Take the book from the top of the cabin.
Turn right and take few steps and then turn right and walk out of the bedroom and walk towards the last room and enter into it and reach the desklamp table.
Turn on the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a book by the light of a DeskLamp.

high_descs: of going straight, turns and goes to the dresser.
There is a book on the table
Book goes straight from the desklamp.
The desklamp turns on when the book is placed on the table.
anns.task_desc: There is a book and the DeskLamp turns on when it is placed on the table
